      "body" : "&quot;Originally called LiveScript, the language was created with syntax that was superficially similar to Java in many ways in order to tap into the Java developer community, though in fact there is no direct relationship between the two languages.&quot; <b>ref:</b> <a href=\"https://www.infoworld.com/article/3441178/what-is-javascript-javascript-and-ecmascript-explained.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">infoworld.com/article/3441178/&hellip;</a>"
